text.text:
‚óèThis is the temple of Maa Bhadrakali,based on whose name City Bhadrak is named.

‚óèThis temple is very beautiful and old architecture of Bhadrak .

‚óèIt is a very peaceful and pious place.

‚óèDevotees from different places visit this temple to pray to Maa Bhadrakali to get her blessings.

‚óèThis temple has also others God's temple inside like Mahapravu Jagannath,Pravu Balabhadra,Maa Subhadra and Mahadev Shiv ji Temple.

‚óèThe walls inside the  temple also bears paintings of  various  of Besha of  Mahapravu Jagannath,Pravu Balabhadra and Maa Subhadra and SAPTAMATRUKA  BESHA of Maa Bhadrakali.

‚óèThis temple also has idols of NABAGRAHA and DASHA MAHAVIDYA.

I would like to suggest that every person must visit Maa Bhadrakali Temple. Her blessings will always keep you happy in your life.

text.text: Jay Maa Bhadrakaliüôè the "Aradhya Devi" of local people of Bhadrak District hence the name Bhadrak. This temple has a huge premise where you will find some other temples such as Jagannath Temple and Shiv temple. A large part of the temple is dedicated for Hawan purposes. Beautiful architecture & separate space for male and female worshippers. Neat and well maintained by the staffs. Huge parking space is available right in front of the temple.

text.text:
Beautiful and old temple in the Bhadrak main city located on the Salandi Bypass road towards Tihidi. Dedicated to Lord Jagannath, Balabhadra, Subhadra & Sudarshan in one premise, Lord Bhadreswara in another and Goddess Baghuasuni in the last.

The temple is well maintained. Apt for various functions like weddings, Upanayan, etc. are done in a systematic way. Separate rooms and Mandap are available for such activities. Required documents are verified for weddings.

Anna prasad is available for eating as well as take away. In ‚Çπ60, you can have good quality Rice, Dal, two types of curry ( I had sajanaa chhuin, alu, baigana, badi besara and buta alu tarkari on 22.02.2022), a khataa and Kheer. One can have as much as he/she likes. Payment through UPI is also available.
